{
  "texts": [
    "In Nawaz et al. (2021), the authors have implemented three models to determine their accuracy.",
    "The first model involved retrieving handmade features from the images during pre-processing, then classification using the closest k-neighbor and Random Forest.",
    "The second model was constructed using CNN deep learning based on the preprocessed data set.",
    "Classifiers such as random forest, nearest k-neighbors, and vector support machines were evaluated.",
    "The third model, AlexNet, was used to derive profound characteristics."
  ]
}